Databases Available from NTIS
by Subscription, Lease, or Purchase

   NTIS offers access to a number of important U.S. Government Databases.
   These databases include all types of information including
     * Bibliographic records of scientific, technical, and business
       information
     * Statistical databases
     * Databases developed from Government collected information

   Choose the data you are interested in:

   Databases for Lease
   Includes important scientific and technical bibliographic databases
   including the NTIS Database

   Online Databases
   Databases that are available for searching on the Web

   Other Databases
   All other types of databases distributed by NTIS for government
   agencies

